title: Oreo Pie
directions: Crush 24 cookies finely; mix with butter. Press onto bottom and up side of 9-inch pie plate.
Chop remaining cookies. Beat pudding mixes and milk in large bowl with whisk 2 min. Stir in COOL WHIP and chopped cookies; spoon into crust.
ingredients: 2 pkg. (3.4 oz. each) JELL-O Vanilla Flavor Instant Pudding
1 tub (8 oz.) COOL WHIP Whipped Topping, thawed
